border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">50</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$14.83 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">150</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$13.67 each</td></tr></tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mt-5 mb-2\">Catalog highlights</h4><ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-[13px] leading-snug\"><li>Fun colorful, full length apron, w/ center pocket &amp; adjustable neck</li><li>Size: 23” W x 34” H, 36&quot; waist ties</li><li>Fabric: 7.5 oz. 65/35 Polycotton twill w/ stain release finish</li><li>8 Color options</li><li>Sold blank, decoration available upon request</li></ul>\n<div class=\"not-prose mt-5\">\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mb-2\">Patch options (supplier)</h4>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600 mb-3\">Options and add-ons from the live Distributor Central product page for this SKU. Pricing may change; confirm on your quote.</p>\n<div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50/30\">\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Product Color</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/5/D/5DE799D368B87F0601A3089707FE90A3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">EF8 Hot Pink</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/0/9/0977D792FD5490953BDB5625AB606BAC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">EF8 Lime Green</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/E/3/E3FF637CB1526BDCC5D40F33400CE50A.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">EF8 Turquoise Blue</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/7/B/7BB08103B41E1E5E92D09FC8E46878D2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">EF8 Purple</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/5/8/58C2A4A7B2478578B7909C05A84FBC59.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">EF8</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">EF8 Royal Blue</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/4/F/4F95A7DE90B491349071D0BA31BAD57F.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">EF8 Mango Yellow</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/D/6/D60670FC6F8CC26103B28F35863EAA58.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">EF8 Charcoal</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/1/2/124F61A760D84EF83AF33DD00D1FFE8D.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">EF8 Olive</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/C/D/CD3F59DEA5D8BD833F3E091FACAB47CD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">EF8 Charcoal Pinstripe</p></div></div>\n</details>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500 mt-4\">Final quote may reflect selected options, proofs, rush, or freight beyond list pricing.</p>\n</div>","salesToolsHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p><strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">Pitch this SKU</strong> — Premium Apron w/ Adjustable Neck &amp; Divided Center Pocket. Lead with use case (uniforms, retail, teams, recognition), then minimums and timeline. Reference included services from “Price includes” in the Description tab when present (e.g. setup, virtual proof, shipping offers).</p>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-2\">\n<li>Quote style <span class=\"font-mono text-neutral-900\">EF8</span> on proposals and POs.</li>\n<li>Offer virtual proofs and artwork checks before production.</li>\n<li>Cross-sell with hats, bags, or jackets for kit programs.</li>\n<li>For decoration and imprint methods, follow supplier notes in the Description tab.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Approved partners can request internal sell sheets, comparison matrices, and margin guidance from the A Design Line team.</p>\n</div>","inventoryHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p>Merchandise is <strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">typically sourced to order</strong>. Stock and availability may vary by supplier and season.</p>\n<p>Supplier-stated production window: <strong>2 days</strong> (not including transit).</p>\n<p>Contact the studio for <strong>rush</strong> feasibility, <strong>split shipments</strong>, or <strong>multi-location</strong> drops before placing large orders.</p>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Minimum order quantity: <strong class=\"text-neutral-800\">25</strong> units (per catalog line).</p>\n</div>"}